libdrawtext
------------------------------------------
libdrawtext is a simple library for fast anti-aliased text rendering in OpenGL.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  libdrawtext-devel-0.4-1bl1
  libdrawtext0-0.4-1bl1
  libfreetype6-2.6.5-1
  libGL1-17.2.6-1
  libGLU1-9.0.0-1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.25.0-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-4
  libtool-2.4.6-5
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jtsiomb/libdrawtext

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jtsiomb/libdrawtext/archive/release_0.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libdrawtext-0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libdrawtext-0.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libdrawtext-0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdrawtext-0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdrawtext0-0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdrawtext-devel-0.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libdrawtext)
  /usr/bin/font2glyphmap.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libdrawtext.README
  /usr/share/doc/libdrawtext/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libdrawtext/COPYING.LESSER
  /usr/share/doc/libdrawtext/README.md

(libdrawtext0)
  /usr/bin/cygdrawtext-0.dll

(libdrawtext-devel)
  /usr/include/libdrawtext/drawtext.h
  /usr/lib/libdrawtext.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libdrawtext.pc

